#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ledgers"
msgstr "Glavne knjige"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Ledgers View"
msgstr "Pogled glavne knjige"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Ledgers View is functionally the data integration center of &kmymoney;. "
"This view is for entering, examining, editing, and deleting transactions in "
"your defined accounts. This view has had a major overhaul since the 5.1 "
"series of &kmymoney; releases. The main difference is that it is now a "
"tabbed display, so you can have more than one account displayed at once. You "
"can actually only see one at a time, but switching by simply clicking a "
"different tab is significantly more convenient than having to select the "
"other account in a dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Pogled Glevne knjige je funkcionalno center za integracijo podatkov "
"&kmymoney;. Ta pogled je namenjen vnašanju, pregledovanju, urejanju in "
"brisanju transakcij v vaših definiranih računih. Ta pogled je bil močno "
"prenovljen od izdaje serije 5.1 &kmymoney;. Glavna razlika je v tem, da je "
"zdaj prikaz z zavihki, tako da imate lahko prikazanih več kot en račun "
"hkrati. Pravzaprav lahko vidite samo enega naenkrat, vendar je preklop s "
"preprostim klikom na drug zavihek bistveno bolj priročen, kot če bi morali "
"izbrati drugi račun v spustnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main display area shows zero or more tabs, each one for the ledger "
"display on one account. The rightmost tab will always have a <guilabel>+</"
"guilabel>. Clicking this will display a dropdown where you can select the "
"account to view, and a new tab will be created for that account. The rest of "
"this chapter will describe using the ledger for any single account."
msgstr ""
"Glavno območje prikaza prikazuje nič ali več zavihkov, vsak za prikaz glavne "
"knjige na enem računu. Skrajno desni zavihek bo vedno imel <guilabel>+</"
"guilabel>. Če kliknete to, se prikaže spustni meni, kjer lahko izberete "
"račun za ogled, in za ta račun bo ustvarjen nov zavihek. V nadaljevanju tega "
"poglavja bo opisana uporaba glavne knjige za katerikoli posamezen račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Ledgers View allows for several key actions: searching and viewing "
"transactions; entering new transaction; and editing, duplicating, deleting, "
"and scheduling existing transactions. Along with this it also provides the "
"ability to move, mark, show additional details for transactions. Other "
"functionality within the Ledgers View includes modifying and reconciling the "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Pogled Glavne knjige omogoča več ključnih dejanj: iskanje in ogled "
"transakcij; vnos nove transakcije; in urejanje, podvajanje, brisanje in "
"razporejanje obstoječih transakcij. Poleg tega ponuja tudi možnost "
"premikanja, označevanja, prikazovanja dodatnih podrobnosti za transakcije. "
"Druge funkcije v pogledu Glavne knjige vključujejo spreminjanje in "
"usklajevanje računa."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>ledgers view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled glavne knjige</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>ledgers view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled glavne knjige</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "The view has three elements:"
msgstr "Pogled ima tri elemente:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The transaction list</para>"
msgstr "<para>Seznam transakcij</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "The filter area, which may or may not be displayed"
msgstr "Območje filtra, ki je lahko prikazano ali ne"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The transaction form, which may or may not be displayed, depending upon your "
"configuration settings as selected in the Configure &kmymoney; Ledger "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec transakcije, ki je lahko prikazan ali ne, odvisno od vaših "
"nastavitev konfiguracije, kot ste jih izbrali v oknu Konfiguriraj &kmymoney; "
"Odsek glavne knjige."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Previous versions of &kmymoney; had a dropdown where you could select the "
"account to be displayed in the ledger. This is no longer necessary, as to "
"view another account, you just open a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Prejšnje različice &kmymoney; so imele spustni meni, kjer ste lahko izbrali "
"račun, ki bo prikazan v glavni knjigi. To ni več potrebno, saj za ogled "
"drugega računa preprosto odprete nov zavihek."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The transaction list</title>"
msgstr "<title>Seznam transakcij</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>ledgers view transaction list</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>seznam transakcij v pogledu glavne knjige</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>ledgers view transaction list</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>seznam transakcij v pogledu glavne knjige</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The transaction list displays all the (possible filtered) transactions in "
"the account. The following columns are always displayed:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam transakcij prikazuje vse (morebitne filtrirane) transakcije na "
"računu. Vedno so prikazani naslednji stolpci:"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:95 details-ledgers.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "the post date, or the actual date the transaction occurred"
msgstr "datum knjiženja ali dejanski datum transakcije"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detail"
msgstr "Podrobnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the category/categories, other account (for transfers,) and memo for the "
"transaction"
msgstr ""
"kategorija/kategorije, drugi račun (za nakazila) in opombe za transakcijo"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payment and Deposit"
msgstr "Plačilo in depozit"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the amount of money either leaving or entering the account in this "
"transaction. A value will appear in one or the other column, as appropriate."
msgstr ""
"znesek denarja, ki zapusti ali vstopi na račun v tej transakciji. Vrednost "
"se prikaže v enem ali drugem stolpcu, kot je primerno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:115 details-ledgers.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This depends on the currently displayed sort order, and will not be "
"calculated if the display is filtered by use of the filter box or "
"transaction status dropdown, as described above."
msgstr ""
"To je odvisno od trenutno prikazanega vrstnega reda razvrščanja in ne bo "
"izračunano, če je prikaz filtriran z uporabo polja filtra ali spustnega "
"menija stanja transakcije, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following columns are optional, and their presence can be toggled by "
"right clicking any column header and selecting or deselecting the "
"appropriate checkbox. Currently, the columns cannot be reordered. The width "
"of a column can be adjusted by using the mouse to grab the line between that "
"column header and the one to its right."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji stolpci so izbirni in njihovo prisotnost je mogoče preklopiti "
"tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete katero koli glavo stolpca in "
"izberete ali počistite izbiro ustreznega potrditvenega polja. Trenutno "
"stolpcev ni mogoče preurediti. Širino stolpca lahko prilagodite tako, da z "
"miško zgrabite črto med glavo tega stolpca in tistim na desni strani."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>No.</title>"
msgstr "<title>Št.</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "the transaction number, which is always optional"
msgstr "številka transakcije, ki je vedno neobvezna"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entry"
msgstr "Vnos"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the Entry Date, which is the date the transaction was entered into the "
"ledger."
msgstr ""
"datum vnosa, ki je datum, ko je bila transakcija vnesena v glavno knjigo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payee"
msgstr "Prejemnik plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the person or organization you are giving money to or receiving money from."
msgstr ""
"oseba ali organizacija, ki ji dajete denar ali od katere prejemate denar."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>C</title>"
msgstr "<title>C</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the Reconciliation Status. The value can be blank, <quote>C</quote> for "
"Cleared, or <quote>R</quote> for Reconciled. The meaning of these terms is "
"discussed further <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.cleared\">below</link>."
msgstr ""
"stanje usklajevanja. Vrednost je lahko prazna, <quote>C</quote> za Počiščeno "
"ali <quote>R</quote> za Usklajeno. Pomen teh izrazov je podrobneje "
"obravnavan <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.cleared\">spodaj</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After a transaction has been entered, it is displayed in the transaction "
"list. You can also change transaction properties or even create new "
"transactions directly in the list. In the transactions list, the default "
"order of transactions is sorted by transaction date, with the most recent "
"transaction on the bottom. Left clicking the header of the transaction list "
"brings up a dialog box that will allow the ability to change the sort order "
"of the transactions. For instructions on how to change the default sort "
"order, see the <link linkend=\"details.settings.register.sorting\">Sorting "
"tab</link> section of the <link linkend=\"details.settings\">&kmymoney; "
"Settings</link> Chapter."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu transakcije se prikaže na seznamu transakcij. Prav tako lahko "
"spremenite lastnosti transakcij ali celo ustvarite nove transakcije "
"neposredno na seznamu. Na seznamu transakcij je privzeti vrstni red "
"transakcij razvrščen po datumu transakcije, pri čemer je zadnja transakcija "
"na dnu. Z levim klikom na glavo seznama transakcij se odpre pogovorno okno, "
"ki omogoča spreminjanje vrstnega reda transakcij. Za navodila o tem, kako "
"spremeniti privzeti vrstni red razvrščanja, glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"details.settings.register.sorting\">Zavihek Razvrščanje</link> v poglavju "
"<link linkend=\"details.settings\">&kmymoney; Nastavitve</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that altering the sort order can be useful in special circumstances, "
"but for many sort orders, especially where the transaction post date is not "
"the first sort key, the balance column will not be very meaningful, and will "
"almost certainly not match the balance of any statement or display by the "
"bank or institution. To minimize confusion, in such cases, the balance "
"column will show all values as <quote>---</quote> and headers which are date "
"dependent (&eg; online balance or reconciliation) are not shown."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je spreminjanje vrstnega reda lahko uporabno v posebnih "
"okoliščinah, toda za veliko naročil za razvrščanje, zlasti če datum "
"knjiženja transakcije ni prvi ključ razvrščanja, stolpec stanja ne bo zelo "
"pomemben in se skoraj zagotovo ne bo ujemal s stanjem kateregakoli izpiska "
"ali prikaza banke ali institucije. Da bi zmanjšali zmedo, bo v takšnih "
"primerih stolpec stanja vse vrednosti prikazal kot <quote>---</quote> in "
"glave, ki so odvisne od datuma (&eg; spletno stanje ali uskladitev), niso "
"prikazane."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In previous versions of &kmymoney; you needed to right-click a column header "
"to change the sort order. Now, right-clicking allows you to toggle display "
"of the optional columns, and you need to left-click to change the sort order."
msgstr ""
"V prejšnjih različicah &kmymoney; ste morali z desno miškino tipko klikniti "
"glavo stolpca, da spremenite vrstni red. Zdaj lahko z desnim klikom "
"preklapljate med prikazom izbirnih stolpcev, morate z levim klikom "
"spreminjati vrstni red."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the transaction list, &kmymoney; displays three values:"
msgstr "Na dnu seznama transakcij &kmymoney; prikazuje tri vrednosti:"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last reconciliation"
msgstr "Nazadnje usklajeno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the most recent date when you reconciled this account. "
"Reconciliation is an important process for many accounts, and is described "
"<link linkend=\"details.reconcile\">in its own chapter</link>."
msgstr ""
"To je zadnji datum, ko ste uskladili ta račun. Usklajevanje je pomemben "
"postopek za številne račune in je opisano <link linkend=\"details.reconcile"
"\">v posebnem poglavju</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cleared"
msgstr "Počiščeno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the total of all cleared and reconciled transactions in this "
"account. See <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.cleared\">this section</link> "
"for more information about the cleared and reconciled states of transactions."
msgstr ""
"To je vsota vseh obračunanih in usklajenih transakcij na tem računu. Glejte "
"<link linkend=\"details.ledgers.cleared\">ta razdelek</link> za več "
"informacij o obračunanih in usklajenih stanjih transakcij."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where &kmymoney; displays the current balance of the account, which "
"is the sum of all transactions in the account. However, if you select more "
"than one transaction in the transaction list, this changes to display the "
"sum of the selected transactions. This returns to the balance when no "
"transactions or only one transaction is selected."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj &kmymoney; prikazuje trenutno stanje na računu, ki je vsota vseh "
"transakcij na računu. Če pa na seznamu transakcij izberete več kot eno "
"transakcijo, se to spremeni in prikaže vsoto izbranih transakcij. To se vrne "
"na stanje, ko ni izbrane nobene transakcije ali samo ena transakcija."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "The filter area"
msgstr "Območje filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In previous versions of &kmymoney;, the filter area was above the "
"transaction list, and it was always displayed. Now, when shown, it is below "
"the list. It is normally hidden, but can be displayed by typing "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap> </keycombo>. At the left of the filter "
"area is a <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"icon-dialog-close.svg\" format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon>dialog close icon. Clicking this will clear any "
"filters in place and hide the filter area."
msgstr ""
"V prejšnjih različicah &kmymoney; je bilo območje filtra nad seznamom "
"transakcij in je bilo vedno prikazano. Ko je prikazan, je zdaj pod seznamom. "
"Običajno je skrit, vendar ga je mogoče prikazati, če vtipkate "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap> </keycombo>. Na levi strani območja "
"filtra je <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"icon-dialog-close.svg\" format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject ></guiicon>ikona za zapiranje pogovornega okna. Če "
"kliknete to, boste počistili vse filtre in skrili območje filtra."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>ledgers view filter area</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>območje filtra pogleda glavne knjige</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>ledgers view filter area</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>območje filtra pogleda glavne knjige</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When displayed, most of the filter area is a text entry box. Typing here "
"will cause &kmymoney; to display only transactions containing the text typed "
"in the box. The text specified can be in any of the fields of the "
"transaction for the displayed account. Clicking the <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"clear text icon at the right end of the text entry box will clear any text "
"that has been entered."
msgstr ""
"Ko je prikazano, je večina območja filtra polje za vnos besedila. Vnašanje "
"tukaj bo povzročilo, da &kmymoney; prikaže samo transakcije, ki vsebujejo "
"besedilo vneseno v polje. Navedeno besedilo je lahko v katerem koli od polj "
"transakcije za prikazani račun. Kliknite ikono čiščenje  besedila <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"na desnem koncu polja za vnos besedila in bo počistil vse vneseno besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the right of the text entry is a status filter dropdown. The default "
"value is <guilabel>Any status</guilabel>, which does not apply any filter to "
"the list. The <guilabel>Not marked</guilabel> and <guilabel>Cleared</"
"guilabel> choices have been previously explained. <guilabel>Not reconciled</"
"guilabel> includes transactions in either of the above groups. There is "
"currently so specific filter for <guilabel>Reconciled</guilabel> "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"Desno od vnosa besedila je spustni meni za filter stanja. Privzeta vrednost "
"je <guilabel>Kateri koli status</guilabel>, ki na seznamu ne uporabi "
"nobenega filtra. Možnosti <guilabel>Ni označeno</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Počiščeno</guilabel> sta bili prej razloženi. "
"<guilabel>Neusklajeno</guilabel> vključuje transakcije v kateri koli od "
"zgornjih skupin. Trenutno obstaja tako poseben filter za "
"<guilabel>Usklajene</guilabel> transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Imported</guilabel> selects transactions which have been imported, "
"even if they have been matched with a non-imported transaction. "
"<guilabel>Matched</guilabel> selects transactions which have been matched, "
"either by &kmymoney; as part of the import process or manually matched by "
"the user. However, once you have clicked <guilabel>Accept</guilabel> on such "
"a transaction, it will not be selected by this filter."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Uvoženo</guilabel> izbere transakcije, ki so bile uvožene, tudi če "
"so se ujele z neuvoženo transakcijo. <guilabel>Ujemanje</guilabel> izbere "
"transakcije, ki so se ujelee bodisi s strani &kmymoney; kot del postopka "
"uvoza ali ročno ujele s strani uporabnika. Ko pa na taki transakciji "
"kliknete <guilabel>Sprejmi</guilabel>, je ta filter ne bo izbral."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Erroneous</guilabel> selects transactions where &kmymoney; has "
"detected some problem. Most commonly, these are <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers.split\">unbalanced transactions</link>, which is often the case for "
"imported transactions where a category was not assigned."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Napačno</guilabel> izbere transakcije, kjer je &kmymoney; zaznal "
"neko težavo. Najpogosteje so to <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.split"
"\">neuravnotežene transakcije</link>, kar pogosto velja za uvožene "
"transakcije, pri katerih kategorija ni bila dodeljena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Scheduled</guilabel> selects upcoming <link linkend=\"details."
"schedules\">Scheduled Transactions</link>. These are displayed in the "
"Transactions List for your convenience, but have not actually been entered "
"into the ledger yet. When you right-click on one of them, the context menu "
"displayed is <guimenu>Scheduled transaction options</guimenu> which is not "
"the same as <guimenu>Transaction options</guimenu> displayed for regular "
"transactions."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Načrtovano</guilabel> izbere prihajajoče <link linkend=\"details."
"schedules\">Načrtovane transakcije</link>. Ti so prikazani na seznamu "
"transakcij za vaše udobje, vendar dejansko še niso bili vneseni v glavno "
"knjigo. Ko z desno miškino tipko kliknete enega od njih, se prikaže "
"kontekstni meni <guimenu>Možnosti načrtovanih transakcij</guimenu>, ki ni "
"enak <guimenu>Možnosti transakcij</guimenu>, prikazan za običajne "
"transakcije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:285 details-ledgers.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "The transaction form"
msgstr "Obrazec transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether or not the transaction form is displayed in the Ledgers View depends "
"on your configuration settings and the type of account being displayed. If "
"present, it includes fields for all the details of a single transaction. It "
"is described in more detail in the following sections."
msgstr ""
"Ali je obrazec za transakcijo prikazan v Pogledu glavne knjige ali ne, je "
"odvisno od vaših nastavitev konfiguracije in vrste računa, ki je prikazan. "
"Če je na voljo, vključuje polja za vse podrobnosti posamezne transakcije. "
"Podrobneje je opisano v naslednjih razdelkih."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it is displayed, the transaction form is a read-only display of the "
"currently selected transaction. It is always at the bottom of the "
"Transactions View, below the filter area, if that is displayed. It is "
"separated from everything above it by a splitter bar, which can be dragged "
"up or down to change the height of the form. If dragged to the bottom, it "
"will hide the form, although the height of the form set that way is not "
"persistent, and will revert to its default when &kmymoney; is restarted. The "
"splitter, like the transaction form itself, is only available when the "
"appropriate configuration to show the form is activated."
msgstr ""
"Ko je prikazan, je obrazec za transakcijo prikaz trenutno izbrane "
"transakcije samo za branje. Vedno je na dnu pogleda transakcij, pod območjem "
"filtra, če je prikazano. Od vsega nad njim je ločen z razdelilno palico, ki "
"jo lahko povlečete navzgor ali navzdol, da spremenite višino obrazca. Če ga "
"povlečete na dno, bo skril obrazec, čeprav tako nastavljena višina obrazca "
"ni obstojna in se bo povrnila na privzeto, ko se &kmymoney; znova zažene. "
"Razdelilnik, tako kot sam obrazec za transakcijo, je na voljo le, ko je "
"aktivirana ustrezna konfiguracija za prikaz obrazca."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering and Editing Transactions"
msgstr "Vnos in urejanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering and editing transactions is now done directly in the transaction "
"list, whether or not the transaction form is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Vnašanje in urejanje transakcij se zdaj izvaja neposredno na seznamu "
"transakcij, ne glede na to, ali je obrazec transakcije prikazan ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fields in the input area match the fields in the transaction list. "
"Additional fields include the Memo field, for a more detailed description or "
"information related to the transaction, and a Category selection. The Split "
"button allows you to <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.split\">split the "
"transaction</link> into multiple categories."
msgstr ""
"Polja v območju za vnos se ujemajo s polji na seznamu transakcij. Dodatna "
"polja vključujejo polje Opomb za podrobnejši opis ali informacije v zvezi s "
"transakcijo in izbiro kategorije. Gumb Razcepi vam omogoča, da <link linkend="
"\"details.ledgers.split\">razcepite transakcijo</link> v več kategorij."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "ledger view direct transaction entry"
msgstr "neposredni vnos transakcij v pogledu glavne knjige"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "ledgers view direct transaction entry"
msgstr "neposredni vnos transakcij v pogledu glavnih knjig"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter a new transaction into the ledger, you can either click the empty "
"entry at the bottom of the ledger list, press <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Ins;</"
"keycombo>, or select the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Transaction</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New transaction...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. To "
"edit an existing transaction, use the &Up; and &Down; arrow keys to navigate "
"through the list. After pressing &Enter; or double-clicking an entry, the "
"transaction list displays the fields required to enter or edit the "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vnesti novo transakcijo v glavno knjigo, lahko kliknete prazen "
"vnos na dnu seznama glavne knjige, pritisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Ins;</"
"keycombo> ali izberete element menija <menuchoice> <guimenu>Transakcija</"
"guimenu > <guimenuitem>Nova transakcija...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Če "
"želite urediti obstoječo transakcijo, uporabite tipke puščic &Up; in &Down; "
"za krmarjenje po seznamu. Po pritisku &Enter; ali ko dvokliknete vnos, "
"seznam transakcij prikaže polja, potrebna za vnos ali urejanje transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the layout of the transaction entry area has been revised in "
"&kmymoney; 5.2. Whether a new transaction is a deposit, withdrawal, or "
"transfer is determined by the data you enter in the amount and category "
"fields. You do not need to explicitly choose a specific tab or specify To: "
"or From:."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je bila postavitev področja za vnos transakcij spremenjena v "
"&kmymoney; 5.2. Ali je nova transakcija polog, dvig ali prenos, je odvisno "
"od podatkov, ki jih vnesete v polja za znesek in kategorijo. Ni vam treba "
"izrecno izbrati določenega zavihka ali določiti Za: ali Od:."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move through the fields press the &Tab; key and when done press &Enter; "
"to save the changes or &Esc; to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Za premikanje po poljih pritisnite &Tab; in ko končate pritisnite &Enter; da "
"shranite spremembe ali &Esc; za preklic."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case the option <guilabel>Use Enter to move between fields</guilabel> is "
"selected, the &Enter; key moves to the next field just as the &Tab; key "
"except for the last entry field where it saves the data."
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Uporabi Enter za premikanje med "
"polji</guilabel>, &Enter; tipka premakne na naslednje polje tako kot &Tab; "
"razen zadnjega vnosnega polja, kamor shrani podatke."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "The fields of a transaction"
msgstr "Polja transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the information using the following notes on the available fields. "
"Note that many fields have <quote>Auto Completion</quote> turned on. That "
"is, if you start typing, &kmymoney; will offer alternatives matching the "
"characters you begin to enter. To select the matching content simply click "
"the entry or press the appropriate keyboard keys. If the entry is not listed "
"finish typing the content to add the new value. The next time you type the "
"content, &kmymoney; will find it for you as you begin to enter the initial "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"V razpoložljiva polja vnesite podatke z naslednjimi opombami. Upoštevajte, "
"da ima veliko polj vključeno <quote>Samodejno dokončanje</quote>. To pomeni, "
"da če začnete tipkati, bo &kmymoney; ponudil alternative, ki se ujemajo z "
"znaki, ki jih začnete vnašati. Če želite izbrati ustrezno vsebino, preprosto "
"kliknite vnos ali pritisnite ustrezne tipke na tipkovnici. Če vnosa ni na "
"seznamu, dokončajte vnos vsebine, da dodate novo vrednost. Ko naslednjič "
"vnesete vsebino, ga bo &kmymoney; našel namesto vas, ko začnete vnašati "
"začetne znake."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note also that the actual fields displayed for a transaction depend on the "
"type of account. For example, <link linkend=\"details.investments.ledger\"> "
"Investment Account transactions</link> include fields for activity type, "
"security, and other investment specific items."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte tudi, da so dejanska polja, prikazana za transakcijo, odvisna od "
"vrste računa. Na primer, <link linkend=\"details.investments.ledger\"> "
"Transakcije naložbenega računa</link> vključujejo polja za vrsto dejavnosti, "
"vrednostni papir in druge postavke, specifične za naložbe."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payer/Payee"
msgstr "Plačnik/Prejemnik plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is who the money comes from or goes to. If the payee is a new entry "
"&kmymoney; will ask if you wish to add this to the list of Payees. Any other "
"information related to a payee or payer, such as address, phone number and "
"account number as well as notes can be updated in the Payees View."
msgstr ""
"To je tisti, od kogar denar prihaja ali h kateremu gre. Če je prejemnik nov "
"vnos, vas bo &kmymoney; vprašal, ali želite to dodati na seznam prejemnikov "
"plačil. Vse druge informacije v zvezi s prejemnikom plačila ali plačnikom, "
"kot so naslov, telefonska številka in številka računa ter opombe, je mogoče "
"posodobiti v pogledu prejemnikov plačil."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category"
msgstr "Kategorija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This specifies an income or expense category for accounting and reporting "
"purposes, and enables you to group certain transactions. Type the name of "
"the category into the defined field. If you have entered the category and it "
"does not exist then &kmymoney; will ask if you want to create a new one. If "
"you select <guilabel>Yes</guilabel> &kmymoney; will then open a dialog box "
"that allows for the further definition of the category based on General, "
"Hierarchy, and Tax characteristics."
msgstr ""
"To določa kategorijo prihodkov ali odhodkov za namene računovodstva in "
"poročanja ter vam omogoča združevanje določenih transakcij. V definirano "
"polje vnesite ime kategorije. Če ste vnesli kategorijo in ta ne obstaja, "
"potem vas bo &kmymoney; vprašal, ali želite ustvariti novega. Če izberete "
"<guilabel>Da</guilabel> &kmymoney; Nato se odpre pogovorno okno, ki omogoča "
"nadaljnjo opredelitev kategorije na podlagi splošnih, hierarhičnih in "
"davčnih značilnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For Transfer transactions, you select the other account in the Category "
"field."
msgstr "Za transakcije prenosov izberete drug račun v polju Kategorija."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to associate parts of the transaction with different categories, "
"&kmymoney; can handle this need. An example might be a cash withdrawal of "
"50, of which you use 10 on food, 20 on beer, and 20 as cash. The transaction "
"will therefore be assigned three categories: Food, Beer, and Cash. To do "
"this, you need to use <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.split\">Split "
"Transactions</link>, which is described in more detail below."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dele transakcije povezati z različnimi kategorijami, lahko "
"&kmymoney; obvlada to potrebo. Primer je lahko dvig gotovine v višini 50, od "
"tega 10 porabite za hrano, 20 za pivo in 20 kot gotovino. Transakciji bodo "
"torej dodeljene tri kategorije: Hrana, Pivo in Gotovina. Če želite to "
"narediti, morate uporabiti <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.split"
"\">Razcepljeno transakcijo</link>, ki je podrobneje opisana spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the special section on <link linkend=\"reference.widgets.category"
"\">&kmymoney; fields</link> for some additional information on how to use "
"this field."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si poseben razdelek o <link linkend=\"reference.widgets.category"
"\">&kmymoney; polja</link> za nekaj dodatnih informacij o uporabi tega polja."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Značke"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags are similar to Categories, and can be used to maintain an orthogonal "
"view to Categories. They provide the ability to group transactions within a "
"Category based on your defined needs. This need could be defined by a "
"specifics to Person, Place, or Thing. For example, you might have a Category "
"for each different type of automotive expenses, and then have a Tag for each "
"vehicle. As with Categories, you can select from the dropdown list, or type "
"a new Tag name, and be prompted if you want to create a new Tag with that "
"name. Within the Tag field &kmymoney; will allow for multiple tags entered "
"within a single transaction. Also, you can enter tags on an individual split."
msgstr ""
"Značke so podobne kategorijam in jih je mogoče uporabiti za vzdrževanje "
"pravokotnega pogleda na kategorije. Omogočajo združevanje transakcij znotraj "
"kategorije glede na vaše opredeljene potrebe. To potrebo bi lahko opredelili "
"s posebnostmi osebe, kraja ali stvari. Na primer, lahko imate kategorijo za "
"vsako vrsto avtomobilskih stroškov in nato oznako za vsako vozilo. Tako kot "
"pri kategorijah lahko tudi tukaj izberete s spustnega seznama ali vnesete "
"novo ime oznake in prikaže se poziv, ali želite ustvariti novo oznako s tem "
"imenom. V polju Značka  &kmymoney; omogoča vnos več značk znotraj ene "
"transakcije. Prav tako lahko vnesete značke na posamezni delitvi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "Memo"
msgstr "Opomba"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single or multi-line memo can be entered if you wish to record any further "
"details of the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zabeležiti dodatne podrobnosti transakcije, lahko vnesete eno ali "
"več vrstic."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Številka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The transaction number can be entered if needed. Note that the check number "
"field can be made visible or invisible in the ledger list if desired. This "
"is configured in the Ledger Settings dialog. While this is most commonly "
"used for a Check Number in a Checking account, it can be used in any type of "
"account, in any way you might want to number your transactions."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi lahko vnesete številko transakcije. Upoštevajte, da lahko polje s "
"številko čeka postane vidno ali nevidno na seznamu glavne knjige, če želite. "
"To je konfigurirano v pogovornem oknu Nastavitve glavne knjige. Čeprav se "
"najpogosteje uporablja številka čeka na tekočem računu, se lahko uporablja v "
"kateri koli vrsti računa, na kakršen koli način, na katerega želite "
"oštevilčiti svoje transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The transaction's date must be entered to specify when the transaction took "
"place. See the special <link linkend=\"reference.widgets\">&kmymoney; "
"fields</link> section for more information on how the date input field can "
"be used to make entering dates quicker and easier. For transactions in "
"checking and credit card accounts, it is your choice whether to use the "
"actual date (when you wrote the check or made the purchase) or the posting "
"date as reported by the bank or credit card company. Using the actual date "
"can help you track when you made the purchase, for example, but the "
"statement or downloaded data from the bank is more likely to use the posting "
"date. &kmymoney; automatically keeps the date the transaction was entered "
"into the ledger, but this is in a different field, which is optionally "
"displayed in the ledger list."
msgstr ""
"Vnesti morate datum transakcije, da določite, kdaj je bila transakcija "
"opravljena. Oglejte si posebno <link linkend=\"reference.widgets"
"\">&kmymoney; polja</link> za več informacij o tem, kako lahko polje za vnos "
"datuma uporabite za hitrejše in enostavnejše vnašanje datumov. Za "
"transakcije na računih s čekovnimi in kreditnimi karticami lahko sami "
"izberete, ali boste uporabili dejanski datum (ko ste napisali ček ali "
"opravili nakup) ali datum knjiženja, ki ga navede banka ali izdajatelj "
"kreditne kartice. Uporaba dejanskega datuma vam lahko pomaga slediti, kdaj "
"ste na primer opravili nakup, vendar je bolj verjetno, da bo izpisek ali "
"preneseni podatki iz banke uporabili datum knjiženja. &kmymoney; samodejno "
"ohrani datum, ko je bila transakcija vnesena v knjigo, vendar je to v drugem "
"polju, ki je izbirno prikazano na seznamu knjige."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note you cannot explicitly enter the Entry Date, which is the date the "
"transaction is actually entered into the ledger. This is always set by "
"&kmymoney;"
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da ne morete izrecno vnesti datuma vnosa, ki je datum, ko je "
"transakcija dejansko vnesena v knjigo. To vedno nastavi &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount"
msgstr "Znesek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, enter the transaction amount into either the <guilabel>Payment</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Deposit</guilabel> field. Note that a simple "
"calculator can be displayed, either by clicking the icon to the right of the "
"field, or by entering the % character into the field, or by entering any of "
"these mathematical symbols: + - * / in a formula, as in <emphasis>12 + 3</"
"emphasis>. When entering the plus sign, the calculator will be opened. Note "
"that only the final result of any calculation will be saved as the Payment "
"or Deposit amount of the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Končno vnesite znesek transakcije v polje <guilabel>Plačilo</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Depozit</guilabel>. Upoštevajte, da lahko preprost kalkulator "
"prikažete s klikom na ikono na desni strani polja ali z vnosom znaka % v "
"polje ali z vnosom katerega koli od teh matematičnih simbolov: + - * / v "
"formuli, kot v <emphasis>12 + 3</emphasis>. Ob vnosu znaka plus se odpre "
"kalkulator. Upoštevajte, da bo samo končni rezultat katerega koli izračuna "
"shranjen kot znesek plačila ali depozita transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are satisfied that all the fields have been adequately filled in, "
"click <guibutton>Enter</guibutton>. If you accidentally press or click "
"<guibutton>Enter</guibutton> before you have finished entering all the data, "
"click <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> to resume entering the data."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste prepričani, da so vsa polja ustrezno izpolnjena, kliknite "
"<guibutton>Enter</guibutton>. Če pomotoma pritisnete ali kliknete "
"<guibutton>Enter</guibutton>, preden končate z vnosom vseh podatkov, "
"kliknite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>, da nadaljujete z vnosom podatkov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>ledgers view transaction form</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled glavne knjige na obrazec transakcije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>ledgers view transaction form</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled glavne knjige na obrazec transakcije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In previous versions of &kmymoney; it was possible to enter or edit data in "
"the Transaction Form. As of version 5.2 the Transaction Form is a read-only "
"display of the transaction selected in the transaction list, possibly "
"showing more details than are displayed in the list above."
msgstr ""
"V prejšnjih različicah &kmymoney; je bilo možno vnašati ali urejati podatke "
"v obrazec transakcije. Od različice 5.2 je obrazec transakcije prikaz "
"transakcije, izbrane na seznamu transakcij, ki je samo za branje in morda "
"prikazuje več podrobnosti, kot jih je prikazanih na zgornjem seznamu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split Transactions"
msgstr "Razcepljene transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The split transaction feature allows you to divide a transaction into "
"multiple categories, representing, for example, the different types of items "
"bought with a single purchase at a store."
msgstr ""
"Zmožnost razcepljene transakcije vam omogoča, da transakcijo razcepite na "
"več kategorij, ki na primer predstavljajo različne vrste predmetov, "
"kupljenih z enim nakupom v trgovini."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A transaction always contains one or more splits. Each split represents "
"money moving into or out of a single account. Most of the time, a "
"transaction contains exactly two splits, one for the account the money is "
"coming from and the other for the account the money is going to. The term "
"<quote>Split Transaction</quote> is used when there are actually three or "
"more splits, when one side of the transaction is further divided into more "
"than one split. This is most commonly done when money moves in or out of a "
"typical bank account, but is allocated to more than one category."
msgstr ""
"Transakcija vedno vsebuje eno ali več cepitev. Vsaka cepitev predstavlja "
"denar, ki se premika na en račun ali z njega. Večino časa transakcija "
"vsebuje natanko dve delitvi, eno za račun, s katerega prihaja denar, in "
"drugo za račun, kamor gre denar. Izraz <quote>Razcepljena transakcija</"
"quote> se uporablja, kadar dejansko obstajajo tri ali več delitev, ko je ena "
"stran transakcije razdeljena na več kot eno delitev. To se najpogosteje "
"zgodi, ko denar prispe na ali z običajnega bančnega računa, vendar je "
"dodeljen več kot eni kategoriji."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a transaction has only one split, it is almost always said to be "
"<quote>unbalanced,</quote> meaning that money is coming from somewhere, but "
"not going anywhere (or vice versa.) Such transactions are typically flagged "
"by being displayed in red in the Ledger. Valid transactions with a single "
"split are usually in Investment Accounts: Add, Remove, or Split shares. The "
"other case is where the amount of the transaction is 0, which banks "
"sometimes produce."
msgstr ""
"Če ima transakcija samo eno razdelitev, se skoraj vedno reče, da je "
"<quote>neuravnotežena</quote>, kar pomeni, da denar prihaja od nekod, vendar "
"ne gre nikamor (ali obratno). Takšne transakcije so običajno označene tako, "
"da se v glavni knjigi prikažejo rdeče. Veljavne transakcije z eno samo "
"delitvijo so običajno v naložbenih računih: Dodaj, Odstrani ali Razdeli "
"delnice. Drugi primer je, ko je znesek transakcije 0, kar banke včasih "
"ustvarijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter a split transaction, create a new transaction, entering the total "
"amount. Then, instead of selecting a category, click the <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"split_icon.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> split icon at the right of the <guilabel>Category</guilabel> field. "
"If you have already selected a category, that becomes the first entry in the "
"split editor."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vnesti razcepljeno transakcijo, z uporabo obrazca za transakcije "
"ali seznama transakcij začnite novo transakcijo, vključno z vnosom skupnega "
"zneska. Nato, namesto da izberete kategorijo, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Razcepi</guibutton> desno od polja <guilabel>Kategorija</"
"guilabel>. Če ste že izbrali kategorijo, postane ta prvi vnos na razdeljenem "
"zaslonu urejevalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display the Split Editor, which shows the Category, Memo, and "
"Payment or Deposit for each split. It also shows the total of the splits, "
"the amount of the transaction, and the difference between them."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo urejevalnik razcepa, ki prikazuje kategorijo, obvestilo in "
"plačilo ali polog za vsako razdelitev. Prikazuje tudi skupni znesek "
"razcepov, znesek transakcije in razliko med njimi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>split editor split with unassigned amount</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>urejevalnik razcepov razdeljen z nedodeljenim zneskom</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>split editor split with unassigned amount</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>urejevalnik razcepov razdeljen z nedodeljenim zneskom</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter a new split or sub-transaction click <guibutton>New</guibutton>, "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Ins;</keycombo>, or double-click an "
"empty row. Double-clicking an existing row lets you edit the split. This "
"will expand the row into form where you can enter or edit a split."
msgstr ""
"Za vnos nove razcepitve ali podtransakcije kliknite <guibutton>Novo</"
"guibutton>, pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Ins;</keycombo> ali "
"dvokliknite prazno vrstico. Če dvokliknete obstoječo vrstico, lahko uredite "
"razcepitev. To bo razširilo vrstico v obrazec, kjer lahko vnesete ali "
"uredite razcepitev."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>split transaction edit form</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>obrazec za urejanje razcepljene transakcije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>split transaction edit form</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>obrazec za urejanje razcepljene transakcije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you specify the category and amount, as well as optional payee, memo, "
"and tag(s). Note that if a payee and memo were entered into the transaction "
"before entering the split editor, they will be included in the first split. "
"It often makes sense to enter a specific memo for each split. This can also "
"be done for the Payee, but it may make more sense to enter that only once "
"for the transaction. To save the split, press <guibutton>Enter</guibutton>. "
"To cancel, press <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj določite kategorijo in znesek ter neobveznega prejemnika plačila, "
"opombo in oznako(-e). Upoštevajte, da če sta bila prejemnik plačila in "
"opomnik vnesena v transakcijo pred vstopom v urejevalnik razcepa, bosta "
"vključena v prvo razdelitev. Pogosto je smiselno vnesti določeno opombo za "
"vsak razcep. To je mogoče storiti tudi za prejemnika plačila, vendar je "
"morda bolj smiselno, da to vnesete samo enkrat za transakcijo. Če želite "
"shraniti to razcep, pritisnite <guibutton>Enter</guibutton>. Za preklic "
"pritisnite <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After entering a split, the bottom of the split editor shows how much of the "
"total transaction is still unassigned. After entering all the splits, press "
"the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button to save the entire transaction. If "
"there is still an unassigned amount, you will be prompted to either return "
"to editing the splits, change the total transaction amount, or leave part of "
"the transaction unassigned. The same is true if the amount is overassigned, "
"in which case the total of the splits is more than the amount of the "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"Po vnosu razcepitve je na dnu urejevalnika razdelitev prikazano, koliko od "
"skupne transakcije je še nedodeljeno. Ko vnesete vse delitve, pritisnite "
"gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da shranite celotno transakcijo. Če še "
"vedno obstaja nedodeljen znesek, boste pozvani, da se vrnete na urejanje "
"razdelitev, spremenite skupni znesek transakcije ali pustite del transakcije "
"nedodeljen. Enako velja, če je znesek dodeljen preveč, v tem primeru je "
"skupni znesek razdelitev večji od zneska transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To redistribute an <quote>Unassigned</quote> or <quote>Overassigned</quote> "
"amount, select the split to be adjusted, and click <guibutton>Apply "
"Difference</guibutton>. If <quote>Unassigned</quote> was previously shown "
"and non-zero, that amount will be added to the selected line item value. If "
"<quote>Overassigned</quote> was previously shown and non-zero, that amount "
"will be subtracted from the selected line item value. As a result, the "
"<quote>Unassigned</quote> or <quote>Overassigned</quote> amount will be set "
"to zero and the transaction can be saved successfully."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prerazporediti <quote>Nedodeljen</quote> ali <quote>Prekomerno "
"dodeljen</quote> znesek, izberite delitev, ki jo želite prilagoditi, in "
"kliknite <guibutton>Uporabi razliko</guibutton>. Če je bil prej prikazan "
"<quote>Nedodeljen</quote> in ni nič, bo ta znesek dodan vrednosti izbrane "
"vrstične postavke. Če je bil prej prikazan <quote>Prekomeren</quote> in ni "
"nič, bo ta znesek odštet od vrednosti izbrane vrstične postavke. Posledično "
"bo znesek <quote>Nedodeljen</quote> ali <quote>Prekomerno dodeljen</quote> "
"nastavljen na nič in transakcijo je mogoče uspešno shraniti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>split transaction in ledger</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>razcepljena transakcija v glavni knjigi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>split transaction in ledger</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>razcepljena transakcija v glavni knjigi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the category field in the transaction form or the transaction list "
"now displays a comma separated list of the categories in each of the split "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da polje kategorije v obrazcu za transakcijo ali seznamu "
"transakcij zdaj prikazuje z vejicami ločen seznam kategorij v vsakem od "
"razdeljenih vnosov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other transaction actions"
msgstr "Ostale dejavnosti transakcij"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing transactions"
msgstr "Urejanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit a transaction, double-click it in the list view, right-click the "
"entry and select <guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem> from the popup menu. or "
"press &Enter; when a transaction is highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti transakcijo, jo dvokliknite v pogledu seznama, z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknite vnos in v pojavnem meniju izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem>. ali pritisnite &Enter; ko je transakcija "
"označena."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting transactions"
msgstr "Brisanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete a transaction, right-click it in the list view and select "
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> from the popup menu when it appears, or "
"click <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> on the transaction form."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati transakcijo, jo kliknite z desno miškino tipko v pogledu "
"seznama in izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem> v pojavnem meniju, ko "
"se prikaže, ali kliknite <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> na obrazcu za "
"transakcijo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matching Transactions"
msgstr "Ujemanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generally, when you import transactions, either via QIF, CSV, OFX, or HBCI, "
"&kmymoney; will automatically attempt to match them against existing "
"transactions. This can be useful for transactions which are created both as "
"Scheduled Transactions, and also imported from your bank or credit card. To "
"allow for differences in the dates, there is a default setting of 4 days, "
"which may be changed in <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"KMyMoney...</guimenuitem> Ledger section, <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"register.import\">Import Tab</link>. Any transactions so matched will be "
"indicated in the ledger with an <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"link.svg\" format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> icon, and on completion of the "
"import, you should review these and either accept or unmatch them."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno, ko uvozite transakcije prek QIF, CSV, OFX ali HBCI, jih bo "
"&kmymoney; samodejno poskušal primerjati z obstoječimi transakcijami. To je "
"lahko uporabno za transakcije, ki so ustvarjene kot načrtovane transakcije "
"in tudi uvožene iz vaše banke ali kreditne kartice. Za upoštevanje razlik v "
"datumih obstaja privzeta nastavitev 4 dni, ki jo lahko spremenite v "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj KMyMoney...</"
"guimenuitem> razdelek Glavna knjiga, <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"register.import\">Zavihek Uvozi</link>. Vse tako usklajene transakcije bodo "
"v knjigi označene z <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"link.svg\" format=\"SVG\" depth=\"1em\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> in po zaključku uvoza jih morate pregledati in "
"jih sprejeti ali preklicati ujemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find that an imported transaction was not automatically matched with "
"an existing transaction when it should have matched, then it is possible to "
"match them manually. Note there is a difference between manually matching "
"two transactions and simply deleting one of them, even though they may "
"appear to have the same effect. Specifically, it is important not to delete "
"the imported transaction, because you will find that the next time you "
"import your transactions, the deleted transaction may show up again. This is "
"because modern import formats like OFX and HBCI use a <quote>Transaction ID</"
"quote> to identify transactions. When you delete the imported transaction, "
"the transaction ID goes with it, so the importer has no way to know this "
"transaction was already imported. For CSV and QIF imports, &kmymoney; "
"creates an identifier for each transaction that is intended to serve the "
"same purpose."
msgstr ""
"Če ugotovite, da se uvožena transakcija ni samodejno ujela z obstoječo "
"transakcijo, ko bi se morala ujemati, jih je mogoče ujemati ročno. "
"Upoštevajte, da obstaja razlika med ročnim povezovanjem dveh transakcij in "
"preprostim brisanjem ene od njiju, čeprav se zdi, da imata enak učinek. "
"Natančneje, pomembno je, da ne izbrišete uvožene transakcije, ker boste "
"ugotovili, da se bo ob naslednjem uvozu vaših transakcij izbrisana "
"transakcija morda znova prikazala. To je zato, ker sodobni uvozni formati, "
"kot sta OFX in HBCI, za prepoznavanje transakcij uporabljajo <quote>ID "
"transakcije</quote>. Ko izbrišete uvoženo transakcijo, gre z njo ID "
"transakcije, tako da uvoznik ne more vedeti, da je ta transakcija že "
"uvožena. Za uvoze CSV in QIF &kmymoney; ustvari identifikator za vsako "
"transakcijo, ki naj bi služila istemu namenu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this happens, the solution is to tell &kmymoney; that the transactions "
"are the same, using the manual matching interface. This allows you to match "
"an imported transaction with a hand-entered (non-imported) transaction. To "
"do so, select one of the transactions to be matched by clicking it, then "
"select the other by clicking it while pressing the <keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap> "
"key, and then select <guimenuitem>Match</guimenuitem> from the context menu. "
"This will match and combine the two transactions. The values of both "
"transactions must be the same for the match to work, except that the dates "
"may differ by the window specified in the settings, as described above."
msgstr ""
"Če se to zgodi, je rešitev, da poveste &kmymoney; da so transakcije enake z "
"uporabo vmesnika za ročno ujemanje. To vam omogoča ujemanje uvožene "
"transakcije z ročno vneseno (neuvoženo) transakcijo. To storite tako, da "
"izberete eno od transakcij, ki jo želite ujemati, tako da jo kliknete, nato "
"izberete drugo tako, da jo kliknete, medtem ko držite tipko <keycap>&Ctrl;</"
"keycap>, nato pa v meniju izberite <guimenuitem>Ujemanje</guimenuitem> "
"kontekstni meni. To bo ujemalo in združilo obe transakciji. Vrednosti obeh "
"transakcij morata biti enaki, da ujemanje deluje, le da se lahko datumi "
"razlikujejo glede na okno, določeno v nastavitvah, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Match transaction dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno ujemanja transakcij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:700
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Match transaction dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno ujemanja transakcij</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since the value is the only field in the two transactions which must "
"absolutely be the same, the value of other fields may differ. Note that "
"although the two Payees may not be identical, they must have been matched by "
"the import process. <guilabel>Match</guilabel>, you will see a "
"<guilabel>Match Transactions</guilabel> dialog. This dialog allows you to "
"choose which of the two transactions is used as the source of the other "
"fields in the matched transaction. Note that if one of the transactions is "
"imported, the date of that transaction will always be used in the matched "
"transaction, even if all other fields are taken from the non-imported "
"transaction. That dialog also gives you the option of reversing the "
"transactions in terms of which is used as a source of fields which differ."
msgstr ""
"Ker je vrednost edino polje v obeh transakcijah, ki mora biti popolnoma "
"enako, se lahko vrednosti drugih polj razlikujejo. Upoštevajte, da čeprav "
"oba prejemnika plačila morda nista enaka, ju mora uvozni postopek ujemati. "
"Ob <guilabel>Ujemanju</guilabel>, boste videli pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Ujemanje transakcij</guilabel>. To pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da "
"izberete, katera od obeh transakcij se uporablja kot vir drugih polj v "
"ujemajoči se transakciji. Upoštevajte, da če je ena od transakcij uvožena, "
"bo datum te transakcije vedno uporabljen v ujemajoči se transakciji, tudi če "
"so vsa druga polja vzeta iz neuvožene transakcije. To pogovorno okno vam "
"daje tudi možnost razveljavitve transakcij v smislu, ki se uporablja kot vir "
"polj, ki se razlikujejo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are happy with the status of the match dialog, click <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton>. The transaction is then displayed as a Matched Transaction in "
"the Ledger. You can then click <guimenu>Transaction</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Accept</guimenuitem> or right-click the matched transaction and "
"select <guibutton>Accept</guibutton> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če ste zadovoljni s stanjem pogovornega okna za ujemanje, kliknite "
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton>. Transakcija je nato prikazana kot ujemajoča "
"se transakcija v glavni knjigi. Nato lahko kliknete <guimenu>Transakcija</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sprejmi</guimenuitem> ali z desno tipko miške kliknete "
"ujemajočo se transakcijo in v kontekstnem meniju izberete "
"<guibutton>Sprejmi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During import of online statements, either directly or by importing a "
"downloaded file, &kmymoney; performs matching as best as it can based on the "
"name of the payee and the amount of the transaction. In case of an invalid "
"match, a matched transaction can be unmatched."
msgstr ""
"Med uvozom spletnih izpiskov, neposredno ali z uvozom prenesene datoteke, "
"&kmymoney; kar najbolje izvede ujemanje na podlagi imena prejemnika plačila "
"in zneska transakcije. V primeru neveljavnega ujemanja se lahko ujemanje "
"transakcije ne ujema."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The matching interface will not allow you to match two transactions which "
"have both been imported. Likewise, it also will not allow matching between "
"two transactions which have both been entered by hand."
msgstr ""
"Vmesnik za ujemanje vam ne bo omogočil ujemanja dveh transakcij, ki sta bili "
"obe uvoženi. Prav tako ne bo dovolil ujemanja med dvema transakcijama, ki "
"sta bili obe vneseni ročno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Understanding the State of a transaction"
msgstr "Razumevanje stanja transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A later section of this handbook discusses <link linkend=\"details.reconcile"
"\">reconciliation</link> in more detail. For now, it is only important to "
"know that transaction can have one of three states: not marked (blank), "
"cleared (C), or reconciled (R). When a transaction is entered, it's state is "
"set to the value specified in the <quote>Data entry</quote> tab of the "
"<quote>Ledger</quote> section of the &kmymoney; configuration dialog, which "
"defaults to <quote>not marked</quote>. Once the bank posts the transaction, "
"the user can mark it as cleared and thus transform it to state (C). Note "
"that these are only a subset of the states described earlier as available in "
"the <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.view.filter\">Ledger Filter</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kasnejši razdelek tega priročnika podrobneje obravnava <link linkend="
"\"details.reconcile\">usklajevanje</link>. Zaenkrat je pomembno le vedeti, "
"da ima lahko transakcija eno od treh stanj: ni označeno (prazno), očiščeno "
"(C) ali usklajeno (R). Ko je transakcija vnesena, je njeno stanje "
"nastavljeno na vrednost, določeno na zavihku <quote>Vnos podatkov</quote> v "
"razdelku <quote>Glavne knjige</quote> datoteke &kmymoney; pogovorno okno "
"konfiguracije, ki je privzeto <quote>ni označeno</quote>. Ko banka "
"transakcijo vknjiži, jo lahko uporabnik označi kot očiščeno in jo tako "
"spremeni v stanje (C). Upoštevajte, da so to le podmnožica prej opisanih "
"stanj, ki so na voljo v <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.view.filter\">Filtru "
"glavne knjige</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>understanding the state of a transaction</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>razumevanje stanja transakcije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>understanding the state of a transaction</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>razumevanje stanja transakcije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you receive a statement from the bank, all cleared transactions should "
"be on the statement. When you reconcile your account, you confirm that the "
"transactions marked Cleared and the transactions listed on the statement are "
"the same, and that the beginning balance plus the sum of the cleared "
"transactions equals the ending balance of the statement. When this is the "
"case, you can 'finish reconciling' which changes the state of all cleared "
"(C) transactions prior to the date of reconciliation to reconciled (R)."
msgstr ""
"Ko prejmete izpisek od banke, morajo biti na izpisku vse očiščene "
"transakcije. Ko uskladite svoj račun, potrdite, da so transakcije, označene "
"kot Prečiščeno, in transakcije, navedene na izpisku, enake ter da je začetno "
"stanje in vsota obračunanih transakcij enako končnemu stanju izpiska. V tem "
"primeru lahko 'dokončate usklajevanje', kar spremeni stanje vseh očiščenih "
"(C) transakcij pred datumom usklajevanja v usklajeno (R)."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to edit a transaction with at least one split marked as "
"reconciled (R), you will be warned. There is a further discussion about why "
"this is important in the section on Reconciliation."
msgstr ""
"Če poskušate urediti transakcijo z vsaj eno delitvijo, označeno kot "
"usklajeno (R), boste opozorjeni. Obstaja nadaljnja razprava o tem, zakaj je "
"to pomembno, je v razdelku o usklajevanju."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Transaction Settings"
msgstr "Spreminjanje nastavitev transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several options that change the appearance and behavior of the "
"Ledgers View in terms of transactions. These settings are found by selecting "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;</guimenuitem> "
"from the menu bar, and selecting the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"ledgers_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> ledger "
"icon from the list on the left."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več možnosti, ki spremenijo videz in vedenje pogleda Glavne knjige v "
"smislu transakcij. Te nastavitve najdete tako, da v menijski vrstici "
"izberete <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;</"
"guimenuitem> in izberete <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject></guiicon> ikono glavne knjige s seznama na levi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the settings are self explanatory. The section linked above has a "
"more detailed explanation of each of the settings. Some of these settings "
"have already been mentioned, but for clarity, several of them are explained "
"briefly below."
msgstr ""
"Večina nastavitev je samoumevnih. V zgornjem razdelku je podrobnejša razlaga "
"vsake nastavitve. Nekatere od teh nastavitev so bile že omenjene, vendar je "
"zaradi jasnosti nekaj izmed njih na kratko pojasnjenih spodaj."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show transaction form"
msgstr "Prikaži obrazec transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting is under the Display tab in the Settings dialog: toggle to hide "
"the transaction form at the bottom of the Ledgers View. The transaction form "
"is now a display only area for the transaction selected in the Transaction "
"List. All entries and edits of transactions are now made directly on the "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev je pod zavihkom Prikaz v pogovornem oknu Nastavitve: "
"preklopite, da skrijete obrazec transakcije na dnu Pogleda glavne knjige. "
"Transakcijski obrazec je zdaj samo območje prikaza transakcije, izbrano na "
"seznamu transakcij. Vsi vnosi in urejanje transakcij se zdaj izvajajo "
"neposredno znotraj seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These images show what direct transaction entry looks like compared to the "
"transaction form."
msgstr ""
"Te slike prikazujejo, kako je videti neposredni vnos transakcije v "
"primerjavi z obrazcem za transakcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "The transaction form:"
msgstr "Obrazec transakcije:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>the transaction form</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>obrazec transakcije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>the transaction form</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>obrazec transakcije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:831
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transactions entered directly:"
msgstr "Transakcije vnesene neposredno:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid "transactions entered directly in ledger"
msgstr "transakcije, vnesene neposredno v glavno knjigo"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid "transaction entered directly in ledger"
msgstr "transakcije, vnesene neposredno v glavno knjigo"

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep changes when selecting a different transaction/split"
msgstr "Ohrani spremembe pri izbiri druge transakcije/razdelitve"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By selecting the next line in the transaction list or split editor, the "
"changes are kept, instead of the default behavior where you have to push the "
"green check mark to save changes."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete naslednjo vrstico na seznamu transakcij ali razdeljenem "
"urejevalniku, se spremembe ohranijo namesto privzetega vedenja, kjer morate "
"za shranjevanje sprememb pritisniti zeleno kljukico."

#. Tag: title
#: details-ledgers.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Transaction Functionality"
msgstr "Druge zmožnosti transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional options are available from the <guimenu>Transaction Options</"
"guimenu> menu, accessed by right-clicking any transaction in the list."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne možnosti so na voljo v meniju <guimenu>Možnosti transakcije</"
"guimenu>, do katerega dostopate z desnim klikom katere koli transakcije na "
"seznamu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-ledgers.docbook:861
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>transaction options sub-menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>podmenu možnosti transakcije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-ledgers.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>transaction options sub-menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>podmenu možnosti transakcije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Options include jumping to the Payees view for the Payee in the transaction, "
"jumping to the Ledgers View for another account in the transaction, creating "
"a schedule based on this transaction, and changing the reconciled or cleared "
"status."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti vključujejo skok na pogled prejemnikov plačila za prejemnika "
"plačila v transakciji, skok na pogled glavne knjige za drug račun v "
"transakciji, ustvarjanje urnika na podlagi te transakcije in spreminjanje "
"usklajenega ali počiščenega stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: details-ledgers.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit the account information from the Ledgers View, select "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> from the menu bar. From the <guimenuitem>Edit "
"Account...</guimenuitem> menu item, you can change the account details. "
"There is also a menu item to bring up the Reconcile menu, which allows you "
"to match transactions against an official bank statement or credit card "
"notice."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti podatke o računu v Pogledu glavne knjige, izberite "
"<guimenu>Račun</guimenu> v menijski vrstici. V meniju <guimenuitem>Uredi "
"račun...</guimenuitem> lahko spremenite podrobnosti računa. Obstaja tudi "
"menijska postavka za prikaz menija Uskladi, ki vam omogoča primerjanje "
"transakcij z uradnim bančnim izpiskom ali obvestilom o kreditni kartici."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<personname><firstname>Michael</firstname><surname>Carpino</surname></"
#~ "personname> <email>mfcarpino@gmail.com</email>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<personname><firstname>Michael</firstname><surname>Carpino</surname></"
#~ "personname> <email>mfcarpino@gmail.com</email>"

#~ msgid "2019-04-02"
#~ msgstr "02.04.2019"

#~ msgid "5.0.3"
#~ msgstr "5.0.3"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The Ledger view is functionally the data integration center of "
#~ "&kmymoney;. This view is for entering, examining, deleting, and editing "
#~ "transactions in your defined accounts. The view is split into three main "
#~ "areas: the filter area, the transaction list, and the input area."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Pogled glavne knjige je funkcionalni center za integracijo podatkov "
#~ "&kmymoney;. Ta pogled je namenjen vnašanju, pregledovanju, brisanju in "
#~ "urejanju transakcij v vaših definiranih računih. Pogled je razdeljen na "
#~ "tri glavna področja: območje filtra, seznam transakcij in območje vnosa."

#~ msgid "Ledger View"
#~ msgstr "Pogled glavne knjige"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You can easily select any account via the account dropdown list at the "
#~ "top of the view area. Note that depending upon the type of the account "
#~ "the <link linkend=\"details.ledger.transactionform\">transaction form</"
#~ "link> at the bottom of the view may change."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Na spustnem seznamu računov na vrhu območja pogleda lahko preprosto "
#~ "izberete kateri koli račun. Upoštevajte, da se <link linkend=\"details."
#~ "ledger.transactionform\">obrazec transakcije</link> na dnu pogleda lahko "
#~ "spremeni glede na vrsto računa."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To the right of the account dropdown list, are two additional fields. The "
#~ "filter box provides the ability to search for matching transactions that "
#~ "will be displayed in the list view. The text specified can be in any of "
#~ "the fields of the transaction for the specific account. The status field "
#~ "is a dropdown list. The status field list allows for the selection of: "
#~ "Any status, Imported, Matched, Erroneous, Not marked, Not reconciled, "
#~ "Cleared, and scheduled transactions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Desno od spustnega seznama računov sta dve dodatni polji. Filtrirno polje "
#~ "nudi možnost iskanja ujemajočih se transakcij, ki bodo prikazane v "
#~ "pogledu seznama. Navedeno besedilo je lahko v katerem koli od polj "
#~ "transakcije za določen račun. Polje stanja je spustni seznam. Seznam polj "
#~ "statusa omogoča izbiro: Poljubno stanje, Uvoženo, Ujemajoče se, Napačno, "
#~ "Ni označeno, Neusklajeno, Prečiščeno in načrtovane transakcije."

#~ msgid "Transaction list"
#~ msgstr "Seznam transakcij"

#~ msgid "<title>The transaction form</title>"
#~ msgstr "<title>Obrazec za transakcijo</title>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "There are two methods of entering transactions into the ledger: using the "
#~ "transaction form or entering the data directly into the transaction list. "
#~ "The transaction form is displayed by default and this is the method we "
#~ "will discuss first. Turning off the transaction form can be accomplished "
#~ "by going to the Ledger section in the Configure &kmymoney; that's within "
#~ "the Settings."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Obstajata dva načina vnosa transakcij v knjigo: z uporabo transakcijskega "
#~ "obrazca ali vnos podatkov neposredno v seznam transakcij. Transakcijski "
#~ "obrazec je privzeto prikazan in to je metoda, o kateri bomo najprej "
#~ "razpravljali. Izklop obrazca za transakcijo lahko izvedete tako, da "
#~ "odprete razdelek Glavna knjiga v razdelku Konfiguriraj &kmymoney; v "
#~ "nastavitvah."

#~ msgid "Using the transaction form"
#~ msgstr "Uporaba obrazca za transakcijo"

#~ msgid "Transaction Form"
#~ msgstr "Transakcijski obrazec"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The transaction form at the bottom of the ledger view is the interface "
#~ "for manually creating transactions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Transakcijski obrazec na dnu pogleda glavne knjige je vmesnik za ročno "
#~ "ustvarjanje transakcij."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Depending upon the type of transaction you wish to enter there are "
#~ "several tabs available on the transaction form. Click on the tab that "
#~ "best defines your transaction (deposit, transfer, or withdrawal) and the "
#~ "form will load several fields available for your input."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Odvisno od vrste transakcije, ki jo želite vnesti, je na obrazcu za "
#~ "transakcijo na voljo več zavihkov. Kliknite zavihek, ki najbolje definira "
#~ "vašo transakcijo (polog, nakazilo ali dvig) in obrazec bo naložil več "
#~ "polj, ki so na voljo za vaš vnos."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Please note that the actual transaction method is not used directly by "
#~ "&kmymoney; but is purely for grouping/reporting purposes."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Upoštevajte, da &kmymoney; ne uporablja neposredno dejanske transakcijske "
#~ "metode; ampak je zgolj za namene združevanja/poročanja."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you are unsure which method to choose simply use Deposit for any money "
#~ "coming into the account, Withdrawal for money going out of the account, "
#~ "and Transfer for money moving from one account to another. The "
#~ "transaction methods and the differences between them are discussed in "
#~ "more detail elsewhere."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če niste prepričani, katero metodo izbrati, preprosto uporabite Depozit "
#~ "za denar, ki pride na račun, Dvig za denar, ki gre z računa, in Prenos za "
#~ "denar, ki se premika z enega računa na drugega. Metode transakcij in "
#~ "razlike med njimi so podrobneje obravnavane drugje."

#~ msgid "Select the transaction method by clicking on the appropriate tab."
#~ msgstr "Izberite način transakcije s klikom na ustrezni zavihek."

#~ msgid "The Tag"
#~ msgstr "Oznaka"

#~ msgid "The Check Number"
#~ msgstr "Številka čeka"

#~ msgid "Directly inputting transactions into the list"
#~ msgstr "Neposredno vnašanje transakcij na seznam"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The second method of entering transactions into the ledger involves "
#~ "editing the transaction list directly."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Drugi način vnosa transakcij v knjigo vključuje neposredno urejanje "
#~ "seznama transakcij."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To do this you must first let &kmymoney; know that you don't want to use "
#~ "the transaction form by opening the settings dialog and unchecking the "
#~ "<guilabel>Show transaction form</guilabel> option."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če želite to narediti, morate najprej dati vedeti &kmymoney; da ne želite "
#~ "uporabljati transakcijskega obrazca, tako da odprete pogovorno okno z "
#~ "nastavitvami in počistite možnost <guilabel>Pokaži transakcijski obrazec</"
#~ "guilabel>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This is performed by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#~ "guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
#~ "menu item and selecting the "
#~ "<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
#~ "\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> </"
#~ "guiicon> register icon from the list on the left. The option to uncheck "
#~ "is labeled <guilabel>Show transaction form</guilabel>. When finished "
#~ "click on <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to be ready to directly enter or edit "
#~ "transactions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "To izvedete tako, da izberete menijsko postavko "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
#~ "&kmymoney;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izberete "
#~ "<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
#~ "\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> </"
#~ "guiicon> registrirajte ikono s seznama na levi. Možnost odkljukanja je "
#~ "označena z <guilabel>Pokaži obrazec za transakcijo</guilabel>. Ko "
#~ "končate, kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da boste pripravljeni na "
#~ "neposreden vnos ali urejanje transakcij."

#~ msgid "Starting the edit"
#~ msgstr "Začetek urejanja"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Which method you use to enter transactions is up to you and is a matter "
#~ "of personal preference."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Katero metodo boste uporabili za vnos transakcij, je odvisno od vas in je "
#~ "stvar osebnih preferenc."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the split editor screen, double-click an empty line to enter a new sub-"
#~ "transaction or press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Ins;</keycombo>. "
#~ "Specify the category, add an (optional) memo, and enter the amount. To "
#~ "save this part of the split, press the green check mark under the "
#~ "category. To cancel, press the red cross."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Na razdeljenem zaslonu urejevalnika dvokliknite prazno vrstico, da "
#~ "vnesete novo podtransakcijo, ali pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul"
#~ "\">&Ctrl;&Ins;</keycombo>. Določite kategorijo, dodajte (neobvezno) "
#~ "beležko in vnesite znesek. Če želite shraniti ta del razdelitve, "
#~ "pritisnite zeleno kljukico pod kategorijo. Za preklic pritisnite rdeči "
#~ "križec."

#~ msgid "Split transactions"
#~ msgstr "Razdeljene transakcije"

#~ msgid "Split transaction"
#~ msgstr "Razdeljena transakcija"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To edit a transaction, select it in the list view and either click on "
#~ "<guibutton>Edit</guibutton> in the transaction form or right click on the "
#~ "entry and select <guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem> from the popup menu. If "
#~ "you are editing transactions directly in the list you can edit the "
#~ "transaction simply by double clicking on an entry or by pressing &Enter; "
#~ "when a transaction is highlighted."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Če želite urediti transakcijo, jo izberite v pogledu seznama in bodisi "
#~ "kliknite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> v obrazcu za transakcijo ali z "
#~ "desno miškino tipko kliknite vnos in v pojavnem meniju izberite "
#~ "<guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem>. Če urejate transakcije neposredno na "
#~ "seznamu, lahko transakcijo uredite preprosto z dvoklikom na vnos ali s "
#~ "pritiskom na &Enter; ko je transakcija označena."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "A transaction can have one of three states: non-reconciled (blank), "
#~ "cleared (C), or reconciled (R). When a transaction is entered, it has "
#~ "state of non-reconciled. Once the bank posts the transaction, the user "
#~ "can clear it and thus transform it to state (C). When you receive a "
#~ "statement from the bank, all cleared transactions should be on the "
#~ "statement."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Transakcija ima lahko eno od treh stanj: neusklajeno (prazno), obračunano "
#~ "(C) ali usklajeno (R). Ko je transakcija vnesena, ima stanje "
#~ "neusklajenega. Ko banka objavi transakcijo, jo lahko uporabnik počisti in "
#~ "tako pretvori v stanje (C). Ko prejmete izpisek od banke, morajo biti na "
#~ "izpisku vse poravnane transakcije."

#~ msgid "Understanding the cleared state"
#~ msgstr "Razumevanje očiščenega stanja"

#~ msgid "cleared state"
#~ msgstr "očiščeno stanje"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Most of the settings are self explanatory. For clarity, several of the "
#~ "settings are explained below."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Večina nastavitev je samoumevnih. Zaradi jasnosti je spodaj razloženih "
#~ "več nastavitev."

#~ msgid "<screeninfo>Transactions entered directly</screeninfo>"
#~ msgstr "<screeninfo>Transakcije, vnesene neposredno</screeninfo>"

